article.headline: Lanier scores 21 in North Florida's 67-58 victory over Maine
article.description: — Chaz Lanier scored 21 points as North Florida beat Maine 67-58 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Lanier scores 21 in North Florida's 67-58 victory over Maine
article.story: JACKSONVILLE, Fla -- — Chaz Lanier scored 21 points as North Florida beat Maine 67-58 on Saturday night. Lanier shot 7 for 12, including 5 for 9 from beyond the arc for the Ospreys (4-2). Ametri Moss added 14 points while finishing 7 of 13 from the floor, and they also had five rebounds. Dorian James shot 4 of 7 from the field and 4 for 4 from the line to finish with 13 points, while adding six rebounds. The Black Bears (3-3) were led in scoring by Kellen Tynes, who finished with 20 points, six rebounds, six assists and four steals. Adam Cisse added 10 points and six rebounds for Maine. AJ Lopez also had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
